story: Pwnky, a creature from the Black night of Inpinity Online, ventured through the digital realms with Dark bad eyes eyes that sparkled with curiosity, a Mechanic body body that shimmered with the essence of creativity, and a Yawning mouth that resonated with the voices of countless creators. On this journey, Pwnky's Golden ears ears fluttered in the electronic winds, and Hidden hair hair flowed like the rivers of code that shaped the landscape. Adorned with a Old captain  hat crafted by the artisans of the net, Pwnky discovered the Horns, a relic that could unlock new realms in this infinite universe.
description: a new Pwnkey with Black night, Dark bad eyes, Mechanic body, Yawning, Golden ears, Hidden hair, Old captain , Horns
